text: Deep Blue Sea 3 is a 2020 science fiction natural horror film starring Tania Raymonde. It is the third installment of the Deep Blue Sea film series, and a direct sequel to Deep Blue Sea 2. ==Plot== ==Cast== * Tania Raymonde as Dr. Emma Collins * Nathaniel Buzolic as Dr. Richard Lowell * Emerson Brooks as Eugene Shaw * Bren Foster as Lucas * Alex Bhat as Spinnaker * Reina Aoi as Miya * Siya Mayola as Bahari * Ayumile Qongqo as Nandi ==Production== Work began on the film in the summer of 2019. The film wrapped production in May 2020. ==Release== The film was released on July 28, 2020 on Digital HD by Warner Bros. Home Entertainment, and was released on Blu-ray and DVD on August 25. ==Reception== On Rotten Tomatoes the film has an approval rating of 69% based on reviews from 13 critics, with an average rating of 5.44 out of 10. Meagan Navarro of Bloody Disgusting expressed that while the film cannot be considered good by conventional standards it was none the less enjoyable. ==See also== * List of killer shark films ==References== ==External links== * Category:English-language films Category:2020 horror films Category:2020 films Category:American action horror films Category:American films Category:American sequel films Category:Direct-to-video sequel films Category:Deep Blue Sea (film series) Category:Warner Bros. direct-to-video films
